inoremap <silent> <A-t> <Esc>:call TermToggle(12)<CR>
tnoremap <silent> <A-t> <C-\><C-n>:call TermToggle(12)<CR>
tnoremap <silent> <Esc> <C-\><C-n>
" tnoremap <C-W> <C-\><C-n><C-W>

" Unmap some stuff cus they're annoying
